title: Mouna Guru
subTitle: Karunakaran is an intelligent youth who cannot tolerate injustice. He leaves his home town and joins a college in Chennai, but soon gets involved with a group of corrupt policemen.

title: Nyayam Ketkiren

title: Filler
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of promotional videos and trailers of Bollywood movies featuring popular actors and actresses.

title: Thithikudhe
subTitle: Separated at youth, Chinnu and Anuradha, two childhood friends turned lovers, reunite years later in an unexpected turn of events..

title: Dindigul Sarathy
subTitle: An average-looking man leads an insecure life. When he constantly suspects his beautiful wife of infidelity, she gets tired of his suspicious nature and decides to leave him.

title: Kidaari
subTitle: Kombaiah Pandian, a village bigwig, falls victim to a brutal stabbing by an enemy. Consequently, his devoted servant Kidari embarks on a mission to unmask the assailant.

title: Polladhavan
subTitle: Prabhu, a middle-class man, saves up to buy a motorcycle but it gets stolen. He goes through multiple hardships in the process of finding his bike.

title: Vaagai Sooda Vaa
subTitle: Veluthambi, who aspired to have a government job, starts teaching poor children in a village. When he learns that they are appointed as bonded labourers, he decides to bring about a change.

subTitle: Selvam, a young man, returns to his village after living abroad and wishes to marry Devayani, an actress and the girl of his dreams. However, things become complicated when she rudely rejects him.

subTitle: Vijay becomes an alcoholic after his wife, Devi, dies while delivering a baby. After he abandons his newborn child, his sister Vijaya starts taking care of his daughter.

subTitle: After falling in love, Vinodh manipulates Tulasi into marriage. However, once their first child is born, he kidnaps the infant, intending to sacrifice him to Satan in a bid to cure his mother.

subTitle: A businessman abandons his first love, to marry a rich heiress. However, things take a turn when his illegitimate son seeks revenge for the injustice done to his mother.

title: Kutti Puli
subTitle: A principled individual inadvertently spoils a contract killer's scheme. Later, he unwittingly becomes the focus of the hitman's vengeful fury.

title: Savaal
subTitle: Brothers Shankar and Raja decide to go to the city for better opportunities post their mother's death. However, they get separated while travelling on a goods train.

title: Adada Enna Azhagu
subTitle: Vasan falls in love with Nisha, the daughter of a politician. When Nisha's father learns about their feelings for each other, he ensures that they do not meet again.

title: Aarumaname
subTitle: When Moorthy, a government officer, dies under mysterious circumstances, his brother, Vaithi, struggles to unravel the truth behind Moorthy's murder.

subTitle: Selvi and Dr Thyagu fall in love and get married, but she is shocked by his family's extravagant spending. Concerned, she warns her husband about their overspending and decides to teach them a lesson.

title: Jore
subTitle: Sakthi falls in love with the daughter of a corrupt politician and later competes with her brother, Vijay, at the college election. Things escalate when Vijay loses and his father gets furious.

title: Oorkavalan
subTitle: Despite protests, Kangeyan helps his brother marry a girl who is engaged to another man. But his brother is soon killed. Trouble ensues when Kangeyan decides to get his brother's widow re-married.

title: Maayandi Kudumbatthar
subTitle: A property dispute ruins the relationship between two brothers, Mayandi and Virumandi. Matters become worse when Mayandi dies and Virumandi's son seeks revenge on his family.

title: Pattiyal
subTitle: Two best friends Kosi and Selvam are contract killers who are given targets by Sami. They fall in love, but their profession becomes a hurdle and the two cannot lead normal lives.
